[2;36m│[0m I have completed initial reconnaissance on the target application. Here are  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m the key findings:                                                            [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m **Application Overview:**                                                    [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - The application is called "Dalgona Challenges"                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - It is a Python Flask application running on Werkzeug/1.0.1 with Python     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 2.7.18                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - The application hostname is "127.0.0.1:32953" targeting port 80            [2;36m│[0m
